    <h1>Passage Ranking</h1>
    <p class="description">Google's system for ranking <strong>individual sections within a long page</strong> — not just the page as a whole. Affects approximately 7% of search queries, rewarding comprehensive guides with multiple ranking opportunities per URL.</p>
